translations.translation:
Abu Ja'far told us.


{He said: Ali ibn Ahmad told us}


He said: Ata' ibn al-Saa'ib reported to us from Abu Khalid from Imam Zaid ibn Ali, peace be upon them both, regarding the words of God Almighty, "And when the eyes turn away" {wa idh zaghat al-absar} - meaning "when they turn away in desire" - "and they are overcome with desire" {wa zulziloo} - meaning "they are tempted and tried".
